    :md
      # Grid
      Here is some short front matter about the grid.

      ## Simple Syntax
      Get started with as few as four classes.

    +exampleWithCode
      include _grid-basic

    :md
      ## Mobile-First & Responsive
      Start with `xs`, then mix and match responsive modifiers.

    +exampleWithCode
      include _grid-responsive

    :md
      ## Automatic Widths
      Leave off a column width if it needs to grow or shrink. The grid will size
      it automatically.

    +exampleWithCode
      include _grid-auto-column-widths
          
    :md
      ## Column Offsets
      Nudge a column to the right with an `-offset` class.
      
    +exampleWithCode
      include _grid-column-offsets
      
    :md
      ## Nesting
      
    +exampleWithCode
      include _grid-nested
      
    :md
